OL,3,CConcerns remain over 'forever
OL,4,Cchemicals' despite 'fully compliant'
OL,5,Cwater supply
OL,7,F"We would like to work with them
OL,8,Fcollectively and then we would like to
OL,9,Faddress the issues of removal."
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News, Health Minister
OL,12,FDeputy Tom Binet says the Government
OL,13,Fis looking at how it can "drastically
OL,14,Freduce" the levels in our water.
OL,16,FHe explains: "It's good news that
OL,17,Fofficially our water is within safe
OL,18,FPFAS limits, but that's only limits
OL,19,Fthat apply at the moment.
